  "2026-05-25T10:00:15.910Z",codex-reliability-agent,"Execution start 2026-05-25: reran duplicate-check/orientation commands (pm context --limit 10, pm search 'reliability lock window in-process runner pm-7rlp pm-uer0' --limit 15, pm list-open --limit 20, pm list-in-progress --limit 20). Reused canonical active items pm-7rlp + pm-uer0 (no duplicate item created). Bootstrap completed per AGENTS.md: npm install -g ., pm --version, node -v, pnpm -v, pnpm build."
  "2026-05-25T10:08:52.505Z",codex-reliability-agent,"In-process runner foundation slice implemented: src/cli/main.ts now exports runPmCli(argv) instead of relying on module-load bootstrapInvocation/void main side effects, and src/cli.ts explicitly imports and invokes runPmCli. Added tests/helpers/cliRunner.ts runInProcessDistCli with captured stdout/stderr, env override, and cache-busted module loading; withTempPmPath now exposes runCliInProcess for parity lanes. Added integration parity coverage in tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts comparing subprocess versus in-process behavior for successful list-open JSON flows and usage-error exit semantics. Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts -t 'keeps subprocess and in-process runner behavior aligned for core flows|keeps Sentry startup lazy for fast CLI commands' --reporter=dot (2 files, target tests passed)."
  "2026-05-25T10:19:47.131Z",codex-reliability-agent,"Verification update 2026-05-25: static-quality gate initially failed due tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts at 7016 lines after adding parity coverage. Resolved by moving parity scenario into new tests/integration/cli-inprocess-runner.integration.spec.ts, re-running focused parity/startup tests, and confirming static-quality gate passes. Full release gate now passes again (1766 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines; docs/static/security/npx-smoke/dogfood/compatibility/observability all green)."
  "2026-05-25T10:22:50.466Z",codex-reliability-agent,"PR opened for combined reliability continuation: #67 https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/pull/67 (branch chore/reliability-lock-window-inprocess-runner-foundation, commit 505c1d01). Entering required >=15 minute AI review window before merge; will process bot feedback then re-verify and merge."
